Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:06.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Um, Sweetie Belle, maybe you should run through steps another few times
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.24,Twilight,,0,0,0,,before you try it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.24,0:00:10.56,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Nope, ready to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.17,0:00:12.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.12,0:00:20.80,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Can't…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.80,0:00:21.72,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,seem…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:22.73,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,to…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.84,0:00:31.78,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I think I threw my neck out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:33.26,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ah, you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.58,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Little more magic practice and lifting brooms will be a сinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.58,0:00:38.76,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I doubt it, that thing weights a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:41.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, has anypony seen my…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.27,0:00:42.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.14,0:00:49.42,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I'll never get my cutie mark for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:50.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:54.92,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But I am happy to keep helping you learn just for the fun of it as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:00:59.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hey, who's gonna clean up this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:01.06,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,This is no mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:03.90,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,These are carefully arranged pieces of the unicycle I took apart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.35,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,and will be putting back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.35,0:01:08.64,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,As soon as Twilight shows me how.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:12.84,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Scootaloo, I've already told you I won't show you how,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:16.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but I'll help you find the instructions so you can figure it out yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:18.59,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I hate research.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:20.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,To your left third shelf from the bottom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:22.48,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You'll find it in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.48,0:01:25.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Thanks so much for helpin' us all learn these new skills, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.74,0:01:29.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Always glad to pass on my love of learning for learning's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.48,0:01:33.40,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Only I'm afraid I'll never get the hang of this potion-makin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:36.55,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Did you follow the magic plant-growing formula I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.55,0:01:37.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.34,0:01:39.69,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,more or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:45.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, let's try it out on this apple seedling and see how we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.54,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I hope this works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:11.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Layin' it on a little thick there, aren't we, pal?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:59.75,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Yahoo, gather around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.53,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,it's time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.56,0:03:05.67,Somepony,,0,0,0,,–  What is that? \N – What's happening? \N – What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:08.35,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,As you all know, I have promised to put on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.35,0:03:12.55,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,an amazing, first-time-ever acrobatic display for you all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.63,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:20.41,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,It's so exciting. But I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.16,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,But… I did not wish to disappoint you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.16,0:03:29.59,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,so I brought my butler Randolph to do that for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:43.09,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Diamond Tiara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.09,0:03:46.39,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I know. I don't know how I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.39,0:03:51.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she get so much attention without even really doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.48,0:03:54.19,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,She's using somepony else to build herself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.19,0:03:57.61,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Without even putting any effort to learn her own skills like we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:04:02.70,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, if we can get really got at the stuff Twilight is teaching us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.98,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,we could be the big shots around here for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.07,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.93,0:04:14.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.39,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.51,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Hey! Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:30.53,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Hey! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Uh? Uh? What? Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.21,0:04:37.20,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I was asking if your sister Rarity will be taking you to Manehatten anytime soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.75,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Because if she is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.75,0:04:43.09,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,maybe you can meet up with us while we hang out with bunch of famous celebrities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:44.24,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:45.55,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Well, that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:47.88,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,pretty nice of you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:52.43,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Actually, my sister hasn't offered to take me to Manehatten anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.78,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,We take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:57.67,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Bump, bump, sugar-love, rump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.91,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:04.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I don't have to go all the way to Manehattan to hang out with the famous and super cool ponies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:07.82,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Me and my friends hang out with Princess Twilight all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.75,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Did you say Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:18.86,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You hang out with her all the time? For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:20.71,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,More like just once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.18,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,She helps us learn cool new stuff to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.18,0:05:24.70,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,That we actually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.70,0:05:26.32,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:31.78,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You must bring me along next time you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.18,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Bring {\i1}us{\i0} along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:36.81,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I mean, we used to see her around town all the time and I thought, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:38.31,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Me too. I thought that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:42.50,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,But now she's a princess, which makes her totally awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.54,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Plus, she has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:46.38,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And she's an alicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.38,0:05:47.29,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,So can I…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:47.85,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,…we…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.85,0:05:48.95,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,…go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.03,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I think we should…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.03,0:05:53.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Would you two excuse us for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:57.50,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We should totally say yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.06,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This is a golden opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.06,0:06:00.25,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't want them laughing at us while I'm mixing potions and accidentally sending plants into choking fits!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:08.36,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,But don't you get it? They have to learn something too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:15.08,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And they won't be able to laugh at us when they're so busy trying to learn stuff of their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:19.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I must admit it's kinda fun to see them working hard to get on the good side for a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.26,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:26.70,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,A princess lives in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.76,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And I'm about to go inside and see her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:31.29,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I can't even tell you how excited I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.86,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,I can't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.94,0:06:36.79,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Now remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:39.90,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Twilight takes this time out with us so we can learn stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.90,0:06:41.78,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Hey there guys, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.36,0:06:47.18,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,It's really her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:49.94,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh, I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.94,0:06:52.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, and… you brought guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:53.69,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:57.64,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight, it is such a thrill and honor to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:06:58.92,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.45,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh. Who dyes your tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.45,0:07:03.64,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,I so have to get that done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.64,0:07:05.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Actually it's not dyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I've always…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.54,0:07:08.06,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And those books in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.06,0:07:10.12,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,What a bold design choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:12.62,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,You should so do that dye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.62,0:07:14.23,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'm all for helping as many ponies as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.57,0:07:22.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But maybe we should keep these weekly visits just between us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.98,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ok. Which one of you wants to practice first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't they go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:32.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,No, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:34.89,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I set up Twilight Time especially for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:36.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.17,0:07:38.63,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's see how your plant potions are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:48.70,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I let you talk us into bringing guests yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:51.40,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear them laugh at us once, Apple Bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.32,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Cause they laughed on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:56.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. We won't make that same mistake again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.84,0:07:58.31,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Oh, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.90,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Look who showed up to make fun of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:04.02,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So much for learning skills to be big shots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.02,0:08:05.61,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Hey, guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:09.54,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,I told everyone about your special Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:12.31,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh no, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.31,0:08:14.44,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And they all want in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.44,0:08:20.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:23.75,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Thanks to me you three are now the hottest thing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:25.31,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.11,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.05,0:08:35.12,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:39.12,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,All these ponies really want to meet Twilight that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.05,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We love you, Cutie Mark Crusaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:48.10,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Now, now, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:53.17,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Demanding time with a princess as an unruly mob simply won't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.83,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest you get organized through us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:59.78,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,The Cutie Mark Crusaders' nearest and dearest friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.29,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Everypony get in line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:04.74,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,No pushing! No pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.80,0:09:08.44,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Of awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:11.20,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.20,0:09:16.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We're really and truly and certifiably the biggest of the big shots in school right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:16.98,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.95,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,They all think we're the greatest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:23.32,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Because we're their tickets to get time with Ponyville's newest and biggest celebrity!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:24.96,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:30.48,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We just said like two seconds ago that inviting two ponies to Twilight time was a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.01,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And now we're supposed to bring the whole class?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.01,0:09:34.13,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.13,0:09:35.32,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:41.12,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I don't like this, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:44.23,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You said not to invite them to Twilight Time, and I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.23,0:09:45.40,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,So what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:47.30,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,This feels like a trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:52.71,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,What's tricky about inviting Twilight out for a meal thanking her for all the nice things she's done for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.31,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Seems like the least we can do for the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.36,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "Princess"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,When I told you when you could come eyeball the Princess at one of her favorite hangouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.92,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I said only two or three of you, tops!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:11.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oops…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:13.40,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,She's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Okay. But stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.80,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,As you wish, Sweetie Belle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:19.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yes. As I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:28.04,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize how hungry I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:31.08,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you asked me to join you here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.08,0:10:32.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm so honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.20,0:10:37.53,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:40.44,Twilight,,0,0,0,,When you first asked me to help you develop new skills, I thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.44,0:10:44.42,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Working with young students so devoted to the joy of learning purely for its own sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:45.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What could be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You all remind me of myself when I was your age!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.06,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Yes, well… we feel the same way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:56.13,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,That's why we invited you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.82,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,All because of our love of learning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.82,0:11:01.35,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.02,0:11:03.48,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Haven't seen you here in, like,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:04.98,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,forever and a half!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.98,0:11:09.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I know. I've been so busy I forgot how delicious everything is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:10.72,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.72,0:11:12.58,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.30,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Oh, nevermind, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:18.04,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.04,0:11:20.29,PinkiePie,,0,0,0,,Nevermind, they're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:33.64,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:37.17,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What in the world is going on out…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:43.61,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What was all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:46.80,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.33,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,When I don't smile in a picture I look sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.09,0:11:52.19,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We're gonna look sad alright…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:01.51,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Can I… help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.60,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Get my picture with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.65,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.38,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Hey! Get out of the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.81,0:12:13.02,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:15.78,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Twilight's gonna be so ticked at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.78,0:12:18.52,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I told ya this was a terrible idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.54,Twilight,,0,0,0,,You seriously all want my autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:23.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.14,0:12:24.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'll sign just a couple more for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.70,0:12:27.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,but then I really must get back to my little friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.37,0:12:31.90,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.90,0:12:33.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Wow, to think…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I've been to the Hayburger so many times,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.01,0:12:38.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,never knowing it's a regular hangout for a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.89,0:12:41.22,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This isn't my regular hangout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:42.88,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to be with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.34,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:49.82,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight decides where it's cool to go based on where {\i1}they{\i0} go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.82,0:12:51.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:53.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks guys, this was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.02,Twilight,,0,0,0,,See ya around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm opening a new lemonade stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:03.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Won't you come to the grand opening?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.73,0:13:08.00,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'll give you free lemonade for a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:10.96,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.65,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,I know exactly how to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:24.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,More lemonade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:25.86,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.09,0:13:32.42,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Done shining your hooves!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:34.06,Somepony,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to do you a favor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:37.96,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Whoa, so bright I can see myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:39.41,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And so can I!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.50,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Nice job bedazzling my bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.74,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,What do I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.29,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Your gratitude is thanks enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:51.98,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,You three must come to my pool party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.98,0:13:54.58,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,It'll be much cooler than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.61,0:13:58.37,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Look who's inviting who to her fancy house!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:01.89,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,I believe we have arrived, Cutie Mark Crusaders.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:09.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is nice, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.40,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,there's no-one else here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:14.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Why is this party cooler, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.46,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Because…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:17.97,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,…of all the ponies we're keeping out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.18,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This has been great, but we have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.25,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It's Twilight Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.36,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,So, we're coming too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:31.97,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.10,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Actually, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.78,0:14:37.46,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We didn't have a chance to ask Twilight, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.46,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.12,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,After all the favors we did for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:44.54,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,After all the favors {\i1}they{\i0} did for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:55.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time!\NTwilight Time! Twilight Time! Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:58.64,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Okay, I know exactly how to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.14,0:15:00.48,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:09.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight time!\NTwilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:12.94,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Go go go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.01,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We gotta beat them to Twilight's so we can explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.22,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,This way! I know a shortcut!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.72,0:15:20.83,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight time!\NTwilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:23.08,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Then we run, like the wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:26.15,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Twilight time!\NTwilight time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.83,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We… made… it…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.24,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Quick! Knock on-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:46.11,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, we can explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.11,0:15:48.49,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,We know you said we should keep Twilight Time to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.49,0:15:51.83,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We didn't mean for so many other ponies to be here! Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:58.34,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I only meant that for your benefit so you could get the most out of our time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.34,0:16:01.71,Twilight,,0,0,0,,But if you want to share your time with others, that's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.26,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,So you're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:05.53,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.53,0:16:07.05,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Come on in, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:09.66,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Spike made nachos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:14.73,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Turns out we'll need some more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:26.81,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Before we start, we should maybe get a bit more organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.81,0:16:29.25,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Ponies interested in magic in this corner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:32.03,Twilight,,0,0,0,,ponies who want to learn potions over here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.03,0:16:34.43,Twilight,,0,0,0,,bookworm ponies over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.36,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:40.29,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Looks like everythin's workin' out just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:43.80,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,And I was so afraid Twilight would be disappointed in us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.55,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Told you I knew exactly how to handle all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:50.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you for taking time out to come learn new things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.38,0:16:52.60,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,Thank {\i1}you{\i0}, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.15,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,We love you, princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.40,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You're awesome, Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.91,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay, let's settle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:00.59,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If you want to thank anypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.59,0:17:05.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,hank the Cutie Mark Crusaders for so generously sharing this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:06.55,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,It was nothing, really,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.55,0:17:08.75,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,we just felt it was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:11.36,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,What a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:13.13,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Let's begin over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.47,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And what would you like to learn, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:19.01,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I want to learn how to become a Cutie Mark Crusader!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:22.56,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And why do you want to become a Cutie Mark Crusader so badly, hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:26.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Because then I could get all my classmates to do me favors and stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,because I'm friends with a famous princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:33.70,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:35.50,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is this true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:39.96,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We wanted our time together just as a way to be with you and learn new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.96,0:17:41.63,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Really and truly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.89,0:17:42.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.35,0:17:48.49,Twilight,,0,0,0,,If it's true, then I'm sure you've all been practicing your skills over the past week.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.49,0:17:50.57,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Show me how much better you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.68,0:17:53.94,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, uh,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:56.26,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,we… can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:59.57,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,We kinda rushed over and forgot to bring our stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:03.29,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.29,0:18:05.40,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Hey everypony, you're in luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.40,0:18:08.58,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,You came to learn, but instead you're getting dinner and a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.34,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Get ready, 'cause we, the Cutie Mark Crusaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.34,0:18:15.97,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,are about to lay on you the amazing skills we learned in Twilight Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.61,0:18:24.27,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, since we don't have Scootaloo's unicycle parts,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:27.89,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,she'll take apart and put back together one of the scooters from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:30.25,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey! That's my scooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.25,0:18:31.99,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,You've got us into this mess, kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:33.71,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,might wanna roll with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:36.93,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Apple Bloom doesn't have an apple seedling,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.47,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,so she'll just grab an apple from the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.85,0:18:44.48,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,And I will begin by using my magic to lift this broom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:03.97,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Become a tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.54,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:19.45,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,That didn't turn out quite as I had hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.29,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Looks like Twilight Time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.29,0:19:26.23,DiamondTiara,,0,0,0,,And look who isn't the princess's entourage anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.14,SilverSpoon,,0,0,0,,Guess they didn't come here to learn after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:34.07,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, neither did any of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.14,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.14,0:19:42.84,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,We made a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:46.46,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,And we really and truly did enjoy learning new skills with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:49.79,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll have to just keep on doing it without you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:51.89,Scootaloo,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:19:58.87,AppleBloom,,0,0,0,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:07.32,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.07,0:20:14.31,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Sweetie Belle?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:20.41,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Remember a moment ago when you asked me to give you a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.45,0:20:36.43,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess Twilight must not be so super-upset anymore,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.43,0:20:39.58,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'cause she's letting us do a diary entry like our sisters do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.58,0:20:42.31,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Boy, did we get our priorities messed up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:46.03,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We started acting special because we were friends with someone special.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.03,0:20:49.43,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We almost forgot the real reason she's special –{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.43,0:20:51.59,SweetieBelle,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because she's our friend.{\i0}
